data.description: Welcome to this stunning carriage-style home, built in 2012, a true embodiment of elegance and comfort! This 2-story masterpiece boasts 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, offering a generous living space of 2,499 square feet including a 3-car garage. Nestled within a resort- style community of MiraBay, this home exudes charm and sophistication, making it the perfect place to call your own.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's dream with 42' cabinets, granite countertops, a vented cooktop fueled by gas, GE Profile Stainless Steel appliances, and built-in double ovens. The glass paned cabinet doors add a touch of class, while the glass etched pantry door enhances both style and functionality.  The master bedroom, conveniently located on the main floor, offers a tranquil retreat with its spacious layout and en-suite bathroom with walk in shower, lots of storage walk in closet, transom windows for added light. The second bedroom can be used as an office or study and has glass French doors for quiet time. Upstairs, a charming loft area awaits, perfect for creating a cozy reading nook or a versatile space to suit your needs. Additionally, you'll find a bedroom and full bathroom with tub on this level, ensuring ample space for family and guests.  Step outside and be captivated by the exquisite outdoor living space. The highlight is the plunge/soaking saltwater pool with enchanting fountains, creating a soothing ambiance for relaxation and entertainment. The pool area with pavered lanai is thoughtfully covered and screened, providing a seamless transition from indoor to outdoor living, all while ensuring privacy and comfort.  This carriage-style home is a true gem, boasts a tankless water heater, plantation shutters throughout, tall ceilings, 8 foot doorways, meticulously designed and crafted with top-notch amenities and finishes. Don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of architectural brilliance, where modern convenience meets classic charm. Come and experience the epitome of luxurious living in this remarkable home. Act fast, as this rare find won't be available for long!  Mirabay is the premier, waterfront, boating community featuring a clubhouse with a cafe, full liquor license, fitness center, swimming pool, slide, clay tennis courts, basketball, parks, and playgrounds. This resort-style community has a community clubhouse, resort-style Olympic swimming pool, 136 ft water slide, parks, 3 playgrounds, gym, cafe with a full liquor license, basketball courts, tennis courts, fitness center, 135-acre lagoon where you can rent kayaks and paddle away, and much more. You will feel like you’re living in a 5-star resort! This community has it all.  Please be advised that there may be audio and video surveillance on site.
